---
import { siteConfig } from "../../site.config";
---

<section class="py-20 px-4">
  <div
    class="max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-14 text-center"
    style={`background: linear-gradient(135deg, ${siteConfig.colors.secondary}, ${siteConfig.colors.secondary}dd);`}
  >
    <h2 class="text-white mb-4 fade-up">Le Signal - Newsletter hebdomadaire</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto fade-up">
      Chaque lundi, l'essentiel de l'impact de l'IA sur l'emploi. Les chiffres, les tendances, les actions concretes. En 5 minutes.
    </p>

    <form id="newsletter-form" class="max-w-md mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 fade-up">
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        required
        placeholder="ton@email.com"
        class="flex-1 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl text-gray-900 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-white transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md"
        style={`background: ${siteConfig.colors.primary};`}
      >
        S'abonner
      </button>
    </form>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-4 fade-up">
      Pas de spam, pas de revente. Desinscription en un clic.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
